<br>
Monk Changes<br>
--------------<br>
We realize the outcry from all the monk changes, however they where necesserry and now we are addressing more issues. Feign Death and double attack are being removed. They simply make monks to powerful. Mend now has a 90% chance to fail at 200+ Skill. We hope these changes affect monks for the better. Monk fists at 65 are now 1/3000, the old ones where overpowering.<br>
<br>
Enchanter Charm Changes<br>
-------------------------<br>
When people solo dragons we know there is a problem (unless a shaman does it) therefor we will be removing ALL charm spells. We realize this is a bit drastic but it IS justified. For compensation you will be recieving burst of flame at 65. This version of burst of flame is resisted 99.9% of the time otherwise it would be overpowered because it does 2 damage.<br>
<br>
Magician Nuke Changes<br>
-----------------------<br>
